nodes.text: Star Wars: Poe Dameron Vol. 4 — Legend Found

Star Wars: Poe Dameron Vol. 4 — Legend Found is a canon trade paperback that collects issues 20–25 of the comic-book series Star Wars: Poe Dameron from author Charles Soule, as well as Poe Dameron Annual 1 from author Robert Thompson. It was published by Marvel Comics on May 15, 2018.
